:''This is a list of genera of biological viruses. See also [[Comparison of computer viruses]].''
This is an alphabetical list of genera of biological [[virus]]es. It includes all [[genera]] of virus listed by the [[International Committee on Taxonomy of Viruses]] (ICTV) 2018 report.<ref name="ICTV">{{cite web |title=ICTV Master Species List 2018a v1 |url=https://talk.ictvonline.org/files/master-species-lists/m/msl/7992 |website=International Committee on Taxonomy of Viruses (ICTV) |accessdate=27 November 2018 |location=Washington, DC |language=English |format=XLSX |date=July 2018}}</ref>
